data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value:
A small utility to hide what you're doing so you can do sketchy stuff.
Controls LEFT ALT Resize the view (hold it down) F3 Toggle distortion F4 Quick show menu F6 Toggle transparency
Images You can use the image menu to select custom image overlays instead of a white background. You can also use the "screencap" feature, which screenshots the current screen and sets that as the custom image overlay instead.
